{"tid":2299490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國總統特朗普批准讓拜登接收總統每日匯報","createTime":"2020-11-24T23:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T03:33:01.000Z","uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2c1fda6bf2bed65f756964840ba6c61d9193e4","tid":2299490,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T23:51:25.000Z","msg":"特朗普和第一夫人梅拉尼婭按感恩節傳統在白宮主持赦免火雞儀式，他發言時感謝醫護人員努力對抗新型冠狀病毒，另外又向保護民眾安全的軍人和執法人員送上祝福，但沒有回答記者問題就離開。<br />\n<br />\n同一日有美國行政官員表示，特朗普簽署相關文件，批准向拜登每日提供最新機密情報，但行政官員仍在處理相關程序，暫時未知道拜登甚麼時候和在甚麼地方聽取匯報。<br />\n<br />\n另外宣稱當選總統的拜登在特拉華州威爾明頓正式介紹獲提名出任國安團隊的六人名單，他強調美國準備在全球舞台再度扮演領導角色，並且會加強同盟友的合作。<br />\n<br />\n另外賓夕法尼州，州長沃爾夫表示，已經簽署確認書，認證拜登在這個州勝出，取得20張選舉人票。<br />\n<br />\n根據美聯社推算，拜登共取得306張選舉人票，超過當選總統門檻。而特朗普就有232張選舉人票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=414152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414152&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKDizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=fc29d9cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414152&h=b4d3a1fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=414152</a>"},{"pid":"65b4ebaeb8ea7a9a4007a8e681d4cd6fdad4ff74","tid":2299490,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T23:52:12.000Z","msg":"未輸，我侵未輸架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb54732c806fe838e09e09ba62b05383a10a0cf","tid":2299490,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"65b4ebaeb8ea7a9a4007a8e681d4cd6fdad4ff74","tid":2299490,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T23:52:12.000Z","msg":"未輸，我侵未輸架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited